Container.Overview:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LinuxServer.io&lt;/strong&gt; Ubuntu base image built with S6 overlay.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After first pull exec into container and run:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;mkdir -p /config/etc/cont-init.d &amp;amp;&amp;amp;  &lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;mkdir -p /config/etc/services.d/baseimage &amp;amp;&amp;amp;  &lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;echo -e '#!/usr/bin/with-contenv bash' &amp;gt; /config/etc/services.d/baseimage/run &amp;amp;&amp;amp;  &lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;echo -e '#!/usr/bin/with-contenv bash' &amp;gt; /config/etc/cont-init.d/30-config&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

